 Shortly before the coronavirus pandemic, actress and Instagram sensation, Patience Yisa, decided to take a break from skit making which made her a hit on various platforms. Sources informed that Patience took a break to repackage by taking delivery of high definition cameras as well as use the opportunity to work on other pending projects in her home state of Benue. Now that there is a gradual opening of the lockdown, the leggy former beauty queen is set and ready to kick off new skits. With many flicks and endorsements to her credit, Yisa is said to be planning on expanding her production company. 